&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic and highly motivated person to join the Trauma and Orthopaedic team to support appointment bookings within department. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
